{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01DEV3dB9BDukNmH6Nqg78PC","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_013dSbg39EqqVt7VzrrfMTk7","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/.session-issues.md","content":"# Session Issues Log — 2026-03-23 (session 3)\n\n### 8-7-rust-otlp-instrumentation — create-story (2026-03-23T11:35Z)\n\n- **Bug found in existing code:** `configureAgent()` falls through to set `agent_sdk: 'traceloop'` for Rust projects — no Rust Traceloop SDK exists. Story task 4 fixes this.\n- **Scope expansion:** AC2 requires writing `OTEL_EXPORTER_OTLP_ENDPOINT` to `.env.codeharness` — current code only writes `OTEL_SERVICE_NAME` there. Necessary for Rust apps that read env vars directly.\n- **Risk: otlp.ts at 375 lines**, will grow to ~410 (exceeds 300-line NFR1 limit). Pre-existing violation.\n- **Risk: AC8 integration-required** — needs real Rust toolchain + `cargo` for full pipeline verification.\n\n### 8-7-rust-otlp-instrumentation — dev-story (2026-03-23T11:50Z)\n\n- **Pre-existing test failures:** 6 tests fail in `modules/sprint/__tests__/migration.test.ts` and `modules/sprint/__tests__/state.test.ts`. Unrelated to story 8-7. May have broken between 8-6 and now.\n- **Mock isolation quirk:** `installRustOtlp` test needed explicit `mockClear()` because `vi.restoreAllMocks()` in `beforeEach` doesn't fully clear `mock.calls` on module-level `vi.mock`'d functions. Minor fragility.\n- **File line count:** `otlp.ts` is now ~423 lines, exceeding the 300-line NFR1 limit. `ensureEndpointEnvVar` duplicates pattern from `ensureServiceNameEnvVar` — could be consolidated.\n- **Sprint-status.yaml corruption:** The dev-story agent overwrote sprint-status.yaml with placeholder content. Had to restore from git and manually set status to `review`.\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":334,"cache_read_input_tokens":51787,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":334},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"8e4c6a49-a8f5-4820-a234-101957ee0803","uuid":"0eddcd4b-8248-44de-93e5-c500b3f9ac19"}
